# Instagram Graph API Access Token
# Instructions:
# 1. Go to https://developers.facebook.com/
# 2. Create an app and select "Instagram Graph API"
# 3. Create an Instagram Business Account (or convert personal to business)
# 4. Generate a long-lived access token with these permissions:
#    - instagram_business_content_publish
#    - instagram_business_manage_messages
# 5. Copy the token and paste it below
# 6. Create a .env file (same as .env.example) and add your actual token

VITE_INSTAGRAM_ACCESS_TOKEN=your_instagram_access_token_here
